    }
  },
  ">>第二道铁门还有20秒打开<<": {
    "translation": "",
    "MultiLang": {
      "US": ">>The second iron gate will open in 20 seconds<<",
      "JP": ">>第二道鉄門は20秒後に開きます<<",
